üòÄüòÄüòÄüòÄüòÄüòÅüòÅ**Please use this form if you are:**
- Moving into Stockport area
- Current Stockport council tax payer moving from one address to another with in the Stockport area
- Current Stockport council tax payer, moving out of the Stockport area
- Current Stockport resident not liable for Council Tax, for example living with parents and moving into their own property.

\*\*If you are a landlord or owner notifying the council of a change to the occupier of a property you own or are a managing agent for, please email council.tax@stockport.gov.uk  with the details.\*\*We will automatically send your details to Council Tax and Electoral Registration and you can choose which other services you would like to notify.If you wish to change your address for a Library membership you can do this via the [Online Library System](https://stockport.spydus.co.uk/cgi-bin/spydus.exe/MSGTRN/OPAC/HOME?HOMEPRMS=HOMEPARAMS).
